Knows and follows digital product design lifecycle and best practices, from doing market research, creating wireframing, prototypes, mockups, and user flow while taking care of Information Architecture (IA);
Skill to understand your project niche and the market type to craft a well-researched digital product design that empathize with target users;
Hands-on experience with industry-leading visual design and design tools;
Work side-by-side with developers to make them understand the design flow, design interaction points, transitions, etc.
Knows and follows agile project management tools, including Azure Boards, Notion, Jira Agile, etc., and agile best practices to meet deadlines;
Well-acquainted with user research and digital product design usability testing best practices;

write down like this for our MERN Stack Developers

Possess deep understanding and application of the MERN Stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) development lifecycle, from market analysis and requirement gathering to developing scalable and high-performing web applications;
Expertise in identifying project specifics and market demands to develop sophisticated, user-centric web applications that resonate with the target audience;
Proficient with leading development tools and technologies in the MERN ecosystem;
Collaborate closely with UI/UX designers to comprehend and implement the envisioned design accurately, ensuring seamless design-to-development handoff and interactive functionalities;
Adept in employing agile project management tools, including Azure Boards, Notion, Jira Agile, etc., and adhering to agile methodologies to streamline development and meet project timelines efficiently;
Skilled in conducting thorough user and market research, implementing feedback into development processes, and rigorously testing web applications to enhance usability and ensure outstanding product quality.
